details.address: 350 W Plaza Dr M, Mooresville, NC 28117
details.description: RegalCha is a vibrant tea and coffee shop in Mooresville, NC, offering a wide variety of boba teas, fruit teas, smoothies, and specialty coffee drinks. Whether you’re craving a refreshing milk tea, a flavorful fruit blend, or a rich iced coffee, we’ve got something for everyone. We use premium ingredients and delicious toppings to deliver a fun and satisfying experience every time. Whether you're stopping by for your daily caffeine fix or a sweet treat with friends, RegalCha is your go-to spot for drinks with a royal twist.

reviews_data.review_text:
Highly recommend this place. Delicious drinks, affordable priced. Each drink  has unique topping come with it. But you can add different one with a little extra charge.
Also sweet level is always my concern. I like sweet treat but not sweet 😂. So i do 25% sweet less ice ( I usually do 2 pumps syrups on Startbuck Grande). So it is perfect for me.  Remember the ice level can affect the sweetness of the drink.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks Ivy! 🥰 So glad you found your perfect sweet & ice combo here—that’s exactly why we offer the custom levels 🧋 Can’t wait to make you another drink soon!

reviews_data.review_text: The drinks/food are so good! The owners are so kind and staff are very welcoming. I wasn’t sure what I wanted and they took the time to help me pick something I’d enjoy. Highly recommend and I will be visiting again!

reviews_data.review_text: Absolutely LOVE RegalCha! 🧋✨ I visited their grand opening in Mooresville and was blown away. The boba is perfectly chewy, the tea is rich and flavorful, and you can really taste the authentic Vietnamese recipe in every sip. The atmosphere is warm and welcoming, and the owners are so kind—it truly feels like a family-run spot with a lot of heart. 💖 Plus, the claw machine adds such a fun touch for extra entertainment! Highly recommend checking them out!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks so much, Mr. Vaughn! Glad you loved everything—we put a lot of heart into it. Can’t wait to have you back again soon (and hopefully you win something from the claw machine next time 😅).

reviews_data.review_text: Newest Boba Tea shop in town and it’s absolutely amazing. The atmosphere was welcoming and fun, the staff were great, and the tea, snacks were delicious. I played the claw machine and failed but it was a fun time. Definitely will be back!!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Haha thanks Morgan! Glad you had a good time (even if the claw machine didn’t cooperate 😅). We’re so happy you enjoyed the drinks, snacks, and vibes. Can’t wait to have you back again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Fab! Love a boba moment and Regalcha delivers! Really good tapioca pearls. Both drinks were best boba I’ve had here in Mooresville.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much, Jake! We’re thrilled you loved the drinks and pearls 💛 It means a lot to hear we’re your favorite boba spot in Mooresville! Can’t wait to see you and Matt again soon for another RegalCha moment 🥰🧋

reviews_data.review_text: I’m so excited for this new boba spot to open! The drinks are delicious, the flavors are super fresh, and you can really tell they put love into every cup.
